<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h1 class="section__title mt-0">About Amara India</h1>
    <p class="section__subtitle mb-0" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      We’re building the future of global trade by combining AI with India’s manufacturing ecosystem.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text);">
      <strong>Amara India</strong> is an AI-powered global trade platform connecting international buyers with verified Indian manufacturers and exporters.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text);">
      Our goal is to make sourcing from India <strong>faster</strong>, <strong>smarter</strong>, and <strong>more transparent</strong> for global businesses. We combine AI supplier discovery, export intelligence tools, a B2B marketplace, and a global sourcing platform—so buyers find the right suppliers and Indian exporters reach the right markets.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text);">
      We’re not just a directory. We’re a technology company focused on trade: verification, data, and AI that help both sides of the transaction make better decisions.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Our platform</h2>
    <ul style="color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>AI supplier discovery</li>
      <li>Export market intelligence</li>
      <li>B2B marketplace</li>
      <li>Global sourcing platform</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-center" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <strong>Get in touch:</strong>
      <a href="mailto:team@amaraindia.com" style="margin-left: 0.5rem;">team@amaraindia.com</a>
    </p>
    <p class="text-center" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <%= link_to "Contact us", contact_path, class: "btn btn--primary" %>
      <%= link_to "Explore products", products_path, class: "btn btn--secondary" %>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
